original_title: Bronx: Gun Hill Road (East) - Reservoir Place
text:
East Gunhill Road, south side, west from Reservoir Place to but not including Tryon Ave. The corner house, in the foreground, bears No. 282 and is called the Clare Evelyn Court. Contiguous to it appears the 5-story Anna Court, bearing No. 272, at the S.E. corner of Putnam Place. Also shown (left) is the west side of Reservoir Place extending south to Reservoir Oval East.

About 1927.
